Blacknightmare::

Blacknightmare had all information that she needed to reprogram 
Orchestra. She started the process. she Added to Orchestra's program 
all Predacon's Program, and as she told him, Orchestra'd remember his 
brothers, his past but he would see all things with a Predacon poit 
of view. 

"It's done" said the femme. she retired the stasis lock and walked 
towards the reprogramation chamber. She opened the door and said "How 
do you feel Orchestra?"
